headline: 3 Dawdling Stocks That Concern Us
summary: Stability is great, but low-volatility stocks may struggle to deliver market-beating returns over time as they sometimes underperform during bull markets.

headline: Are Homeowners Overpaying on Property Taxes? Now They Can Find Out on Realtor.com®
summary: Many homeowners could be overpaying their property taxes and not even know it. In fact, 40.5% of properties in the U.S. may be overassessed, according to a new Realtor.com® Property Tax Report. And, today, for the first time on a major real estate platform, homeowners can not only uncover potential savings, they can get the evidence they need to challenge over-assessed property values through a new tax protesting resource on Realtor.com®.
